{"tid":354041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【問你死未】 明年6月30日前所有網絡支付必須移至人行平台處理","createTime":"2017-08-10T06:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T14:47:21.000Z","uid":7222,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e99df8ccaf84b8b44e6748ed02faa9dbc381097","tid":354041,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"人民銀行 8 月 4 日發出通告，所有網絡支付業務至 2018 年 6 月 30 日前，必須全部遷移至人行旗下的網聯平台處理。這也意味第三方支付行業中存在多年的直連模式，進入倒數計時，支付寶、財付通等超級金融夢想將成泡影。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報導，人行在通知中指出，各銀行和支付機構應於今年 10 月 15 日前，完成接入網聯平台和業務遷移的相關準備工作；此後網聯將進行接入工作，最終在 2018 年 6 月 30 日起，支付機構受理的涉及銀行帳戶網絡支付業務，全部通過網聯平台處理。<br />\n<br />\n這意味著某種程度上，央行把整個支付體系納入監管目的已經達到，至於落實的進程只是時間問題。同時也意味著清算市場終將由銀聯一家獨大轉變為多頭競爭的局面。<br />\n<br />\n據《財經韜略》分析，以後第三方支付由「網聯清算有限公司」來負責，銀聯只佔網聯 1.55% 的股權。而銀聯的核心業務 -- 銀行卡清算業務將門戶洞開，隨著當局的對外開放，Visa、萬事達、美國運通全面殺入信用卡市場。Visa(V-US) 已向中國央行遞交建立銀行卡清算機構的資格申請，萬事達組織、美國運通也打算跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.cnyes.com/news/id/3887035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F3887035&d=Ussnp9FXOmovNdWbrxaexP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b4f8e1da\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.cnyes.com/news/id/3887035</a><br />\n<br />\n以業務管理的角度來看，央行把第三方支付完全收編，支付寶、財付通等超級金融夢想將成泡影。<br />\n<br />\n一窺網聯清算公司股權結構，公司第一大股東是央行，第二大股東 (梧桐樹) 是外管局的投資平台；第三方支付機構中，財付通獲得跟支付寶平起平坐的地位，京東則躋身第 5 大股東，第 6 至第 10 大股東也全是央行的人馬。<br />\n<br />\n由此可知，央行透過組建網聯，把對第三方支付的控制權牢牢抓在手中，網聯平台是央行強加給第三方支付的一個中介機構，所有金融往來和交易都將在央行的如來佛掌中。且央行通過網聯能夠獲得更多的金融大數據，終結支付寶、財付通等機構「數據寡頭」壟斷現象。<br />\n<br />\n網聯的推出，對傳統銀行是利多，它們未來將不再被「第三方支付寡頭」奴役。但對支付寶和財付通們來說則是利空，雖然這兩大巨頭各佔接近 10% 的網聯股權，但對某些人洗錢就不太方便了。<br />\n<br />\n銀聯則是最大苦主，國際信用卡組織 Visa 等殺進中國後，預示著銀聯在中國的壟斷地位將受到強大的挑戰，畢竟 Visa、萬事達、美國運通等組織個個都是狠角色，來頭也不小，它們都是美國的信用卡組織。<br />\n<br />\n據《2017 年 BrandZ 全球最具價值品牌百強榜》公布的數據顯示，Visa 以 1109.99 億美元的品牌價值排行第 7 名。<br />\n<br />\n這將讓中國的銀行業產生重大變局。據業內預計，中國將在 2020 年成為全球最大的銀行卡市場，屆時流通中的銀行卡數量預計將從 2016 年的 60 億張增長到 90 億張。如此龐大的市場，美國 3 大巨頭發卡組織早已垂涎欲滴，摩拳擦掌準備分一杯羹。<br />\n<br />\n但中國的銀行業也不是吃素的，隨著互聯網、物聯網、人工智能的快速興起，中國銀行業的大變革早已如火如荼的展開。"},{"pid":"f3041c1006aab20075410512e11907630c1738ee","tid":354041,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"玩完<br />\n即係又係玩返信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ee76850aea32b479bc8b9d132aa6864c73936b","tid":354041,"uid":39200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"大陸最鍾意就係見你做起哂, 百花齊放嘅時候就收左你"},{"pid":"8977b156a24484bce749a93c26bf6f12ca0fc6ee","tid":354041,"uid":22706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"即係支付寶微信支付通通唔俾搞，收歸國有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a61d77be583ed8e5f2481d28acea06634a5f51","tid":354041,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係支付寶微信支付通通唔俾搞，收歸國有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔算係<br />\n野要繼續做，但big data要些牙埋比國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de34390d9f14893b9db9b82b66916e55dc35cefb","tid":354041,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩完<br />\n即係又係玩返信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0068512862b75b15d823bd76640619df8614baf9","tid":354041,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係支付寶微信支付通通唔俾搞，收歸國有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔算係<br />\n野要繼續做，但big data要些牙埋比國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全面鎖國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13eb0f5101782aa6630a3bfbcc7b53148d70890a","tid":354041,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"冇咩影響，只係被納入監管範圍，同埋支付寶等民間金融機構，唔可以無限制咁擴大。"},{"pid":"7511ea698084b9417a2ca33619761d9bd70e17a4","tid":354041,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"好賤,又監管"},{"pid":"9abd8b2d3657fa1d7c976c84ded24eb8a48c49c8","tid":354041,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好賤,又監管</blockquote><br />\n邊度做生意都要監管嫁啦"},{"pid":"9344f975e979651df0ee696392799396d16bb331","tid":354041,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<br />\n共產黨流氓本性盡現<br />\n等你做起左就一野收割你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偏偏永遠都有人感謝黨俾飯佢食，唔知道原來碗飯要連本帶利咁還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8fded8391b0cf0fdfdd74d070933894da9cdbc","tid":354041,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑撚死<br />\n共產黨流氓本性盡現<br />\n等你做起左就一野收割你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偏偏永遠都有人感謝黨俾飯佢食，唔知道原來碗飯要連本帶利咁還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇黨批准你做，你連做起的機會都冇。<br />\n<br />\n而家又唔係唔俾你做，只係唔可以俾你一個人玩哂。<br />\n<br />\n中共自己都交出銀聯籌碼，作出交換。<br />\n<br />\n監管的代價，就係開放俾外資進入中國市場。如果冇監管點可能俾你入。"},{"pid":"21f29c2ddb18343e4e7b3bce4d23cc1531ced4da","tid":354041,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"五毛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96879aab0a0da47c5ea9f54f970c484aaeb11f42","tid":354041,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>笑撚死<br />\n共產黨流氓本性盡現<br />\n等你做起左就一野收割你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偏偏永遠都有人感謝黨俾飯佢食，唔知道原來碗飯要連本帶利咁還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇黨批准你做，你連做起的機會都冇。<br />\n<br />\n而家又唔係唔俾你做，只係唔可以俾你一個人玩哂。<br />\n<br />\n中共自己都交出銀聯籌碼，作出交換。<br />\n<br />\n監管的代價，就係開放俾外資進入中國市場。如果冇監管點可能俾你入。</blockquote><br />\n笑撚死，咁係咪無黨批准你食飯就連飯都無機會食？所以食飯前要感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於你話開放俾外資進入？聽住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入世貿果陣夠話公平貿易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60b3e36af2775235dfa404116b92353b9c01315","tid":354041,"uid":7222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好賤,又監管</blockquote><br />\n邊度做生意都要監管嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n監管為名，監控為實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b626393dfd2764e39598f47824acda23c4ddaa","tid":354041,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>笑撚死<br />\n共產黨流氓本性盡現<br />\n等你做起左就一野收割你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偏偏永遠都有人感謝黨俾飯佢食，唔知道原來碗飯要連本帶利咁還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇黨批准你做，你連做起的機會都冇。<br />\n<br />\n而家又唔係唔俾你做，只係唔可以俾你一個人玩哂。<br />\n<br />\n中共自己都交出銀聯籌碼，作出交換。<br />\n<br />\n監管的代價，就係開放俾外資進入中國市場。如果冇監管點可能俾你入。</blockquote><br />\n笑撚死，咁係咪無黨批准你食飯就連飯都無機會食？所以食飯前要感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於你話開放俾外資進入？聽住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入世貿果陣夠話公平貿易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢D比較嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n金融點可能任由私人資本掌握？尤其中國呢個國家係由黨建立。<br />\n<br />\n點解唔開放？外資進入都要接受政府的監管。<br />\n<br />\n仲有呢個世界冇所謂的公平貿易，否則憑中資的資本，咩都買到啦。"},{"pid":"4761e4b5e0d189e0526bf71cebaf92010fff8372","tid":354041,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好賤,又監管</blockquote><br />\n邊度做生意都要監管嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n監管為名，監控為實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊做生意都要接受人哋政府管轄。<br />\n<br />\n中國過去外國買嘢收購，進入人哋的市場都一樣要接受人哋政府的審批，規管。<br />\n<br />\n做咩外國監管就啱，中國就唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107de71a77e8888f78eab3f81c57f9985c3697f4","tid":354041,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好賤,又監管</blockquote><br />\n邊度做生意都要監管嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n監管為名，監控為實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊做生意都要接受人哋政府管轄。<br />\n<br />\n中國過去外國買嘢收購，進入人哋的市場都一樣要接受人哋政府的審批，規管。<br />\n<br />\n做咩外國監管就啱，中國就唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩外國銀行既申報係由銀行跟法例有要求時先報，或者監管機構要查野先會講<br />\n<br />\n支共係每一個人每一條trade，有冇犯法嫌疑都要俾支共知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰平台係佢控制，分分鐘可以隨意唔俾人轉錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/161506_ecf7aaa4c937ca87a490dd7ac8bdcfb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F161506_ecf7aaa4c937ca87a490dd7ac8bdcfb0.jpg&h=55813791&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/161510_cf5f5e000c8b5ecba1f6864280e234f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F161510_cf5f5e000c8b5ecba1f6864280e234f1.jpg&h=2862ef5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6efeca10498d4bc4d33d8ddc79ddff57820f81d","tid":354041,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好賤,又監管</blockquote><br />\n邊度做生意都要監管嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n監管為名，監控為實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊做生意都要接受人哋政府管轄。<br />\n<br />\n中國過去外國買嘢收購，進入人哋的市場都一樣要接受人哋政府的審批，規管。<br />\n<br />\n做咩外國監管就啱，中國就唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩外國銀行既申報係由銀行跟法例有要求時先報，或者監管機構要查野先會講<br />\n<br />\n支共係每一個人每一條trade，有冇犯法嫌疑都要俾支共知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰平台係佢控制，分分鐘可以隨意唔俾人轉錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/161506_ecf7aaa4c937ca87a490dd7ac8bdcfb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F161506_ecf7aaa4c937ca87a490dd7ac8bdcfb0.jpg&h=55813791&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.