nail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F161510_cf5f5e000c8b5ecba1f6864280e234f1.jpg&h=2862ef5b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國政府唔知？斯諾登而家可以返美國，光明正大做人未？根本個個國家都會mon住自己嗰場。有冇犯法你做咩都會俾政府知。<br />\n<br />\n有問題外國一樣可以唔俾你做交易，唔係要監管機構做咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鳩噏完未<br />\n就算香港<br />\n股票交易申報都係以broker為單位申報，唔係每一個人每一個客都報<br />\n銀行唔熟但我所知都係類似<br />\n<br />\n斯諾登唔關事講黎把撚</blockquote><br />\n點唔關事？斯諾登事件就係證明左咩都有監管監控。<br />\n<br />\n你唔報就冇監控？我寧願好似中共咁講明監控你。好過班鬼佬口講話冇，乜數據都send哂去政府嗰ser。"},{"pid":"25b64d5ad75f6e97c3988faed141be558bff8827","tid":354041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n邊度做生意都要監管嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n監管為名，監控為實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊做生意都要接受人哋政府管轄。<br />\n<br />\n中國過去外國買嘢收購，進入人哋的市場都一樣要接受人哋政府的審批，規管。<br />\n<br />\n做咩外國監管就啱，中國就唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩外國銀行既申報係由銀行跟法例有要求時先報，或者監管機構要查野先會講<br />\n<br />\n支共係每一個人每一條trade，有冇犯法嫌疑都要俾支共知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰平台係佢控制，分分鐘可以隨意唔俾人轉錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/161506_ecf7aaa4c937ca87a490dd7ac8bdcfb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2F